<section class="rp-styleguide__section">
  <h2>Philosophy</h2>
  <p>
    Our design system follows <strong>Korean Neo-Minimalism</strong> principles, emphasizing:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Clarity</strong> - Information hierarchy with clean typography</li>
    <li><strong>Efficiency</strong> - Minimal cognitive load for all users</li>
    <li><strong>Subtlety</strong> - Soft colors and gentle interactions</li>
    <li><strong>Accessibility</strong> - WCAG 2.1 AA compliance from the ground up</li>
  </ul>
</section>

